---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Free Agile AI Prompt Playbook';
const pageDescription = 'Get 5 copy-paste AI prompts that make you sound technical in sprint planning, refinement, and retrospectives—even if you\'ve never touched ChatGPT before.';
---

<LandingLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <!-- Hero Section - Compact, ~523px height -->
  <section class="bg-[#1a1a1a] py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1350px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left Column - Text Content -->
        <div>
          <!-- Main Headline -->
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 mt-[50px]">
            <span class="text-white">How I Got Rehired in </span>
            <span class="text-[#294bf3]">2 Weeks</span>
            <span class="text-white"> After Being Laid Off With Thousands of Other Scrum Masters</span>
          </h1>

          <!-- Hook statement -->
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            When companies started cutting "ceremony-only" agile roles in January 2023, I built automation systems that proved I was technical—not "just a facilitator."
          </p>

          <!-- Value proposition -->
          <p class="text-base lg:text-lg text-white mt-3">
            This <span class="text-[#294bf3] font-semibold">free playbook</span> is your first step to proving technical value.
          </p>

          <!-- CTA Button - scrolls to email form -->
          <a
            href="#get-playbook"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#1e3acc] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#294bf3]/50 scroll-to-form"
          >
            Download the Free Playbook
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column - YouTube Video -->
        <div>
          <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <iframe
              width="100%"
              height="100%"
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YOUR_VIDEO_ID"
              title="Danny's Agile Automation Story"
              frameborder="0"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
              allowfullscreen
              class="w-full h-full"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Crisis Story Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1350px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-8">
        My Layoff Should Have Been Career-Ending. Instead, I Was Back at Work in 2 Weeks.
      </h2>

      <div class="text-lg text-[#1a1a1a] leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p>In January 2023, companies made a choice:</p>

        <p>Keep the agile professionals who "just facilitated meetings" or keep the ones who "built technical systems."</p>

        <p>I was laid off along with thousands of other Scrum Masters. My peers spent months searching for interviews. Some are still looking.</p>

        <p class="font-semibold">But I was back at work within two weeks—landing a Fortune 500 pharmaceutical role.</p>

        <p class="font-bold">The difference?</p>

        <p>In every interview, I could say:</p>

        <blockquote class="inline-block text-left border-l-4 border-[#294bf3] pl-6 py-2 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-r-lg italic max-w-2xl">
          "I've built Jira automation systems that saved my last team 12 hours per sprint. I don't just coordinate work—I architect solutions that create measurable value."
        </blockquote>

        <p>That's not facilitation. That's technical proof.</p>

        <p class="font-bold text-[#294bf3]">So I made a different choice. I built systems that made me indispensable.</p>

        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <a
          href="#get-playbook"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#1e3acc] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#294bf3]/50 scroll-to-form"
        >
          Get the Free Playbook
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Inline Email Form Section -->
  <section id="get-playbook" class="bg-[#f0f7ff] py-16 lg:py-20 scroll-mt-8">
    <div class="max-w-[1350px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 lg:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] text-center mb-4">
          Start Phase 1: Get the FREE Agile AI Prompt Playbook
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-8">
          5 copy-paste AI prompts that make you sound technical in sprint planning, refinement, and retrospectives—even if you've never touched ChatGPT before.
        </p>

        <!-- What's Inside the Playbook -->
        <ul class="text-left space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">The Story Improver Prompt</strong> — Turn vague requirements into crystal-clear user stories with acceptance criteria in 30 seconds</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">The Acceptance Criteria Builder</strong> — Generate testable, specific acceptance criteria that developers actually understand</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">The Refinement Prep Assistant</strong> — Prepare for refinement in 5 minutes instead of 2 hours—with all edge cases covered</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">The Sprint Summary Generator</strong> — Auto-summarize sprint outcomes for stakeholders without manual report writing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">The Retrospective Theme Analyzer</strong> — Identify patterns from retro notes instantly—spot what's working and what needs attention</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Email Form with ConvertKit -->
        <form action="https://app.convertkit.com/forms/FORM_ID/subscriptions" method="post" data-sv-form="FORM_ID">
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email_address"
            placeholder="Enter your email"
            class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-lg border border-gray-300 rounded-lg text-[#1a1a1a] placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#294bf3] focus:border-transparent"
            required
          />
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full mt-4 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#1e3acc]"
          >
            Download the Free Playbook
          </button>
        </form>

        <!-- Social Proof -->
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center mt-6">
          Join <strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">15,000+ agile professionals</strong> who've downloaded this playbook. Takes 2 minutes to read, saves hours every sprint.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof Statement Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1350px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-8">
        My Automation Systems Never Stop Working. They Don't Take Sick Days. They Just Create Value.
      </h2>

      <div class="text-lg text-[#1a1a1a] leading-relaxed">
        <p class="mb-6">While other Scrum Masters were updating Jira tickets manually, my automation systems were:</p>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 inline-block text-left">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Syncing sprint dates automatically</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Prepping standup updates before meetings</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Flagging blockers 3 days before they became crises</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Sending stakeholder reports without human intervention</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mb-4">I quickly realized this wasn't just about efficiency—it was about separating your value from your hours.</p>

        <p class="font-bold text-xl mb-8">Companies don't want coordinators anymore. They want architects who build systems.</p>

        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <a
          href="#get-playbook"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#1e3acc] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#294bf3]/50 scroll-to-form"
        >
          Start with the Free Playbook
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Comes After Section - Teaser -->
  <section class="bg-[#f8fafc] py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1350px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#294bf3] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">After the Playbook</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] text-center mb-4">
        The Complete Transformation System
      </h2>

      <!-- Intro paragraph -->
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The Prompt Playbook teaches you to <strong>sound</strong> technical. The complete system (available after you opt-in) teaches you to <strong>BE</strong> technical with:
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Button - Above cards -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <a
          href="#get-playbook"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#294bf3] rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#1e3acc] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#294bf3]/50 scroll-to-form"
        >
