          <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The Sprint Sync Engine, 12-Minute Standup, Stale Ticket Radar, and automated reporting systems that saved my teams 12+ hours per sprint—and got me hired in 2 weeks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white/70 p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-left border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
